More than 100 people have gathered at Cows Corner in Colleen Glen in a show of solidarity for Black Monday.
The convoy which includes vehicles from various neighbourhood watch groups, farmers and other supporters are making their way along the N2 to John Tallant before coming back.
This is a developing story.

